<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VR Tourism Home</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: url('<%= asset_path('549551.jpg') %>');
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }
        header {
            background-color: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.8);
            color: white;
            padding: 2.5em;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            position: relative;
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        header nav {
            margin-left: auto;
        }
        header nav a {
            color: white;
            margin: 0 1em;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        main {
            padding: 2em;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 3em auto;
            text-align: center;
        }
        section {
            margin-bottom: 2em;
        }
        .world-wonders {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1em;
        }
        .wonder {
            position: relative;
            background-color: rgba(245, 245, 245, 0.9);
            padding: 1em;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .wonder img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .wonder h3 {
            margin-top: 0.5em;
        }
        .wonder .historical-data {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            transform: translateY(100%);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .wonder:hover .historical-data {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        .wonder:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        .get-started {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5em 1em;
            background-color: #43b0f1;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 1em;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .get-started:hover {
            background-color: blue;
        }
        .world-wonders-title {
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Media queries for responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 1200px) {
            header {
                padding: 1.5em;
            }
            main {
                padding: 1.5em;
                margin: 2em auto;
            }
            .world-wonders {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            header h1 {
                position: static;
                transform: none;
                margin-bottom: 1em;
            }
            header nav {
                margin-left: 0;
            }
            header nav a {
                display: block;
                margin: 0.5em 0;
            }
            .wonder {
                padding: 0.5em;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            header {
                padding: 1em;
            }
            main {
                padding: 1em;
                margin: 1em auto;
            }
            .get-started {
                padding: 0.5em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to VR Tourism</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
            <a href="/register">Register</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Explore Virtual Tours</h2>
            <p>Experience amazing places from the comfort of your home.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="world-wonders-title">World Wonders</h2>
            <div class="world-wonders">
                <div class="wonder">
                    <img src="<%= asset_path('360 View/col.jpg') %>" alt="Colosseum">
                    <h3>Colosseum</h3>
                    <p>Step back in time to the grandeur of Rome's ancient amphitheater.</p>
                    <div class="historical-data">
                        The Colosseum, completed in AD 80, was the largest amphitheater ever built and could hold up to 80,000 spectators.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="wonder">
                    <img src="<%= asset_path('360 View/petra.jpg') %>" alt="Petra">
                    <h3>Petra</h3>
                    <p>Discover the rose-red city carved into the cliffs of Jordan.</p>
                    <div class="historical-data">
                        Petra, established possibly as early as 312 BC, was the capital of the Nabataean Kingdom.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="wonder">
                    <img src="<%= asset_path('360 View/taj.jpg') %>" alt="Taj Mahal">
                    <h3>Taj Mahal</h3>
                    <p>Admire the beauty of this white marble mausoleum in India.</p>
                    <div class="historical-data">
                        The Taj Mahal, completed in 1653, was commissioned by Emperor Shah Jahan in memory of his wife Mumtaz Mahal.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="wonder">
                    <img src="<%= asset_path('360 View/Mp.jpg') %>" alt="Machu Picchu">
                    <h3>Machu Picchu</h3>
                    <p>Explore the lost city of the Incas, perched high in the Andes Mountains.</p>
                    <div class="historical-data">
                        Machu Picchu, built in the 15th century, served as an estate for the Inca emperor Pachacuti.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="wonder">
                    <img src="<%=  asset_path('360 View/Ci.jpg') %>" alt="Chichen Itza">
                    <h3>Chichen Itza</h3>
                    <p>Marvel at the pyramid of Kukulkan and other wonders of this Mayan city.</p>
                    <div class="historical-data">
                        Chichen Itza, a large pre-Columbian city, was built by the Maya people and thrived from AD 600 to the 1200s.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="wonder">
                    <img src="<%= asset_path('360 View/christ-the-redeemer.jpg') %>" alt="Christ the Redeemer">
                    <h3>Christ the Redeemer</h3>
                    <p>See the iconic statue overlooking Rio de Janeiro.</p>
                    <div class="historical-data">
                        Christ the Redeemer, completed in 1931, is a colossal statue of Jesus Christ in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="wonder">
                    <img src="<%= asset_path('360 View/gwc.jpg') %>" alt="Great Wall of China">
                    <h3>Great Wall of China</h3>
                    <p>Walk along the ancient walls stretching over 13,000 miles.</p>
                    <div class="historical-data">
                        Built between the 7th and 16th centuries, the Great Wall of China was intended to protect the Chinese states and empires from various nomadic groups.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <a class="get-started" href="/login">Get Started</a>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
                